<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

	<PropertyGroup>
		<Description>
			Shared abstractions for Kafka telemetry in NetMetric. Defines interfaces and models for retrieving Kafka client statistics,
			consumer lag snapshots, and structured metrics for producers and consumers. Supports testability, pluggable sources, and typed snapshot processing.
